Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H312F8D&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Terrible Weapon Targets the Three Riders!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,434)\fs52\fscy120}Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Amamiya, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Nero, of GOD's Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-That you, Keisuke?\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato sent\Nus a private telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone called Amamiya has the ninth RS\Nblueprint piece, and he's flying in to Haneda today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amamiya? How will we recognise him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he'll have a red attaché case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A red attaché case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Amamiya?\N-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is something wrong?\N-I think someone's watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-The blueprint?\N-Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done your job. Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised, Jin Keisuke? I, Tiger Nero, have\Ninherited the blood of the tyrant Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, be a good boy and\Ngive me that attaché case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to play with you.\NWe'll settle this some other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you really think\Nthe blueprint piece is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the real attaché case right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, Jin Keisuke is our prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. You truly are the Villain\NArmy's ace in the hole, Tiger Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm humbled by your praise, King Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of Amamiya's attaché case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right here!\N-Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the genuine article! That makes\Ntwo pieces in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining seven are with\NJin Keisuke; Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Jin Keisuke's body searched,\Nbut he didn't have any more on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Find them! Use any means necessary\Nto secure those blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke's still not been in touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he managed to\Nmeet up with Mr. Amamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hear this, Tachibana Toubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The ace of GOD's Villain Army, Tiger Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tiger Nero?\N-Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All it would take to hang Jin\NKeisuke right now is one little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why, you--!\N-There's only one way to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your seven blueprint pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-He didn't give them to us!\N-Do you think I'm blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you one minute\Nto decide. Just one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take any longer than that\Nand Jin Keisuke is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke's only got one minute to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!\N-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do...\Nis hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they have the blueprints, at least\NKeisuke will be alive to get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If the worst happens to Keisuke, we\Nwon't be able to protect the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know he'll pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're here to escort you.\N-Fold up those blueprints and come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've got everything arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? I'm\Nnot gonna let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Now, give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Untie Keisuke first.\NThat was the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, they're the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let Keisuke go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke is GOD's archenemy.\NNaturally, he'll be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,B-blast you! We had a deal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD doesn't make deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazami Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirou! You're here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform... V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-There!\N-The chains, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-I can't transform with my hands tied!\N-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those chains are made from a\Nspecial alloy! You'll never break them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, I can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thanks, V3.\N-Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Nero! Hand over those blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle this another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Tornado Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Blast...\N-He's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the blueprints? Don't lie to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord... Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work, Tiger Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The RS Device blueprints, at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's complete, I'll promote\Nyou to GOD's chief executive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly honoured, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin production of the RS Device at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One slip-up, and now they\Nhave all the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a chance we\Ncan get them back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It'll take them some time\Nto put the RS Device together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing we need\Nto do is find their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did manage to plant a tracker on one\Nof their agents when they captured me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Their base is as good as found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Aren't you done yet?\N-We just need to install the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-King Dark awaits. Hurry up!\N-Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, Tiger Nero sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an unidentified radio\Nwave transmitting from this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-They must've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-But we've got the direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kamen Riders X and V3.\NWe've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that--?\N-The RS Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised? Thanks to you giving back\Nthe blueprints, the RS Device is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara's horrifying RS Device can instantly\Nbreak down any matter on a molecular level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the H-bomb can't compare to\Nthe energy unleashed by this process.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happens when\NI switch on the RS Device?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It can obliterate anything from an industrial\Ncomplex to a major city in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I give you two a test\Nrun first? Control energy output!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-V3...\N-We have to stop that device.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready? Prepare for activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kamen Rider V3, the rest is up to you.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the blueprints. I'll destroy\Nthat thing if it means my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! That's a job\Nfor my generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-But I have to--!\N-Alright, together then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-what happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider #2. Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I infiltrated GOD's lab a\Nwhile back, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The vital blueprint for the\NRS device's core is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirty spy! Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you my transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,#2!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Tornado Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran away, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Tiger Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness... We destroyed the RS device.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have that last blueprint piece, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do well to remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With unexpected aid from #2 and V3,\Nthe RS Device has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Dark has sworn a terrible revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD have finally gathered all of Dr. Nanbara's\Nblueprints to complete the RS Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider will risk his life to destroy it, but\Nthe gigantic King Dark seems insurmountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Farewell, X Rider"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider